reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 6, 2017
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Still hands down the best diapers we've found
reviews.reviewText: We had our son abroad, and when we returned to the U.S. we tried several brands of diapers here, finding them all to be disappointing when compared to the Merries. They're thick, absorbent, and leak-free, but still seem breathable, comfortable, and are easy to change. The quality of the materials and manufacturing is simply on a different level from the other options we've tried here. Glad we were able to find them online.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Very good quality, my newborn son has an allergy to Pampers and had bad diaper rash from pampers. After we tried Huggies, but because of bad diaper rash, Huggies did not work. Merries help to prevent diaper rash.

I told my husband about these diapers from my home country and we went ahead and bought them.They work wonders. It's comfortable for her and super absorbant!
